    <title>冰糖雪梨</title>
    <link href="/2022/10/03/%E5%86%B0%E7%B3%96%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%A8/"/>
    <url>/2022/10/03/%E5%86%B0%E7%B3%96%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%A8/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="冰糖雪梨的做法"><a href="#冰糖雪梨的做法" class="headerlink" title="冰糖雪梨的做法"></a>冰糖雪梨的做法</h1><h2 id="食材"><a href="#食材" class="headerlink" title="食材:"></a>食材:</h2><ol><li>一个大白梨 </li><li>银耳</li><li>红枣</li><li>冰糖</li><li>枸杞</li></ol><h2 id="做法"><a href="#做法" class="headerlink" title="做法:"></a>做法:</h2><ol><li>先把梨洗干净，可以表面搓盐洗。</li><li>把银耳洗干净后用温水泡发。</li><li>将梨沿着头部切开，切开后去掉里面的核，注意可以用勺子，会比刀安全一点。</li><li>将一个大枣、4~8个枸杞、两颗冰糖洗干净后和泡发的银耳一起放进掏空的大白梨中。</li><li>往梨中加入适量的水后盖上切掉的梨头，加入蒸锅中蒸30min。</li><li>用牙签插梨感觉梨软了以后可以出锅食用。</li></ol><h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考:"></a>参考:</h2><p>b站妙招姐《教你冰糖雪梨的正确做法，润肺止咳，做法简单，大人小孩都爱喝》<sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV11E411h7k2/?is_story_h5=false&p=1&share_from=ugc&share_medium=android&share_plat=android&share_session_id=9599f247-a702-4e08-9edd-05982ab5e9ae&share_source=WEIXIN&share_tag=s_i&timestamp=1664758324&unique_k=o991YfV">[1]</span></a></sup></p><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV11E411h7k2/?is_story_h5=false&amp;p=1&amp;share_from=ugc&amp;share_medium=android&amp;share_plat=android&amp;share_session_id=9599f247-a702-4e08-9edd-05982ab5e9ae&amp;share_source=WEIXIN&amp;share_tag=s_i&amp;timestamp=1664758324&amp;unique_k=o991YfV">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV11E411h7k2/?is_story_h5=false&amp;p=1&amp;share_from=ugc&amp;share_medium=android&amp;share_plat=android&amp;share_session_id=9599f247-a702-4e08-9edd-05982ab5e9ae&amp;share_source=WEIXIN&amp;share_tag=s_i&amp;timestamp=1664758324&amp;unique_k=o991YfV</a><a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
